# Local secrets for chain test scripts.
# Copy this file to `.env` (same directory) and fill in values.
# `.env` is gitignored — do NOT commit it. Do NOT paste values into chat.
#
# Loaded automatically by chain_test_v2.py at import time. Real env vars
# (set in your shell) take precedence over values in this file.

